text: Temple on Dr.Rajkumar Road, Kalyanagiri Kalyanagiri is a suburb of Mysore city in Karnataka state of India. ==Location== Kalyanagiri is located on the eastern side of Mysore city.https://www.google.co.in/maps/place/Kalyanagiri,+Mysuru,+Karnataka/@12.3250397,76.6799703,15z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x3baf71b36882ec0b:0x55694ac74b906972!8m2!3d12.3251887!4d76.6889136 ==Demographics== Kalyanagiri is a predominantly Muslim area with many mosques and madhrassas around. The Hindu population is also sizeable. ==See also== * Mysore East ==References== Category:Suburbs of Mysore
title: Kalyanagiri
